rComments: He is by far my favorite teacher ever.  He makes class interesting, and is genuinely interested in the subject matter and his students.  He's not an EASY grader, but is fair and will help you do your best work.  I would love to be in another of his classes again, and reccommend him highly.
Maxwell was the coolest guy. He totally respects original thinking, and that's the best way to go in his class.
Great can-do attitude!  I know this may sound funny... but sometimes I would daydream in class (not that his lectures were boring or anything) that he was my private dancer.
watch out for his dangerous "blue steel" glance. finger licking good.
